{"tid":323194,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"想做廢中但俾家人屌到仆街點算好","createTime":"2017-07-15T12:01:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-15T15:15:46.000Z","uid":20241,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8e1000b90e070b62a946c89058bd1ab70bbded21","tid":323194,"uid":20241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T12:01:32.000Z","msg":"我份人就hea底<br />\n小學成日考全級頭3<br />\n但中學開始染上打機惡習成績一落千丈<br />\n大學畢業後打幾份垃圾工都係搵萬幾<br />\n而加人到中年三十幾都無咩有用既工作經驗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實我每個月洗4-5千到就夠，主要係食飯+上網電話水電費，其他無咩太大物慾<br />\n興趣得打機同儲高息股 好似d人儲玩具咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  成日FF間野自己都有份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 去睇下啲人做到隻狗幫公司搵到錢再分俾我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實一路都好想將香港層樓放租<br />\n跟住番台灣做個廢中 係山邊海邊租間屋仔日日宅係度打機上連登就夠 得閒悶就做下pt 俾人屌就屌鳩番啲客同老世轉頭<br />\n但層樓係家人送既 佢地一聽到我想咁就起曬鋼屌我不思進取<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唉諗起日日番份廢工真係好愁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n人到中年又唔知做邊行可以重頭來過<br />\n大家有無建議<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7838af99869c887b0b4862d311fe13afeb112c08","tid":323194,"uid":121771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T12:17:11.000Z","msg":"我以為你會講得閒會叫<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c2875ebd7db55ac6656005c9cb11c7ab3ea20dd","tid":323194,"uid":20241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T12:23:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我以為你會講得閒會叫<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n打J啦<br />\n一陣有病就仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bb4863d95282ccd56ed7c27815691d04de38dae","tid":323194,"uid":121771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T12:36:12.000Z","msg":"其實 最緊要 搵一份同自己專長 掛鉤嘅工. 我都係成30歲先搵到一份 